  <source>Oslo University Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with uveal malignatnt melanoma with liver metastases have a dismal prognosis with a
      median survival of less than 12 months. There is noe established treatment showing increased
      overall survival. In this study we will determin if liver transplantation will result in
      long term survival in patients with liver only metastases from uveal malignant melanoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
